name: EDENStories.OpeningTheAlbums
description:
EDEN Stories is a mediarchaeological narrative composed of images in Videotex. The whole story is accessible by alternately consulting objkt and hicetnunc.

Format: PNG based on Videotex (used to encode the information of the French MINITEL, used from 1980 to 2012).
Dimension : 320 x 250 px.
Color: Greyscale.
